  "detailed_description": "<h1>Read Manual Please.</h1><p><strong><u>First, read our manual before you play. At the moment, there are no tutorials, which can make it difficult to play.</u></strong><br>Click on the 'View the manual' button on the right or go to the folder where the game is installed.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Tower of Arcana is a single player deck-action game that combines card games and action rogue-lites. Build your deck, fight enemies to get cards and equipment, and conquer the tower of gods!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2></strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/bc4d9923bc20f31a6c5c4bb0cf4f7b30.poster.avif?t=1606167187\" width=600 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/bc4d9923bc20f31a6c5c4bb0cf4f7b30.webm?t=1606167187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/bc4d9923bc20f31a6c5c4bb0cf4f7b30.mp4?t=1606167187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>Deck Building : </strong></i>Choose your card for battle. As you climb the tower, you can discover more cards and add them to your deck. Battle through various cards and reach the top.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/78bc5b30f4e22a84a7b10039f9bfe905.poster.avif?t=1606167187\" width=600 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/78bc5b30f4e22a84a7b10039f9bfe905.webm?t=1606167187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/78bc5b30f4e22a84a7b10039f9bfe905.mp4?t=1606167187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>Battle : </strong></i>Battle your enemies using the cards you have configured. Each card has a cool time and a cost. We hope you enjoy your card.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/eb43985688e9ba900a60d810c3cc760c.poster.avif?t=1606167187\" width=600 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/eb43985688e9ba900a60d810c3cc760c.webm?t=1606167187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/eb43985688e9ba900a60d810c3cc760c.mp4?t=1606167187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>Unlock : </strong></i>You can unlock the card by earning points earned through play. Unlocking will allow you to collect that card the next time you play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/cac0e43d677089bf9dd97ebde43ffa4f.poster.avif?t=1606167187\" width=600 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/cac0e43d677089bf9dd97ebde43ffa4f.webm?t=1606167187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206730/extras/cac0e43d677089bf9dd97ebde43ffa4f.mp4?t=1606167187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>Equips : </strong></i>Enhance your strength by wearing equipment. It will help you conquer the tower.",
